Description:
   Cloak:precision is the Swordsman's signature remort cloak. Rather than
   providing damage reduction or avoidance like other cloaks, it instead
   reduces the effectiveness of critical hits against the Swordsman.

   The cloak provides two benefits:
     - Critical Chance Reduction: Enemies' critical hit chance against the
       Swordsman is reduced by pseudo_level / 5 percentage points. At
       pseudo-level 100, this is a 20% reduction in crit chance.
     - Critical Damage Reduction: When an enemy does land a critical hit,
       the bonus critical damage is reduced by 25%.

   Both effects apply to physical and spell criticals alike. This makes the
   Swordsman exceptionally resilient against burst damage from critical
   strikes.

   Duration scales with pseudo-level (pseudo_level / 8 rounds).
